00061

00064    }
00065

00067       fMeanChannel.fT0Coef        = TMath::Mean(nChannels, &vT0Coef[0]);
00068       fMeanChannel.fT0CoefErr     = TMath::RMS (nChannels, &vT0Coef[0]);
00069       fMeanChannel.fDLWidth       = TMath::Mean(nChannels, &vDLWidth[0]);
00070       fMeanChannel.fDLWidthErr    = TMath::RMS (nChannels, &vDLWidth[0]);
00071       fMeanChannel.fBananaChi2Ndf = TMath::Mean(nChannels, &vBananaChi2Ndf[0]);
00072       fRMSBananaChi2Ndf           = TMath::RMS (nChannels, &vBananaChi2Ndf[0]);
00073 
00074       fMeanOfLogsChannel.fBananaChi2Ndf = TMath::Mean(nChannels, &vBananaChi2NdfLog[0]);
00075       fRMSOfLogsBananaChi2Ndf           = TMath::RMS (nChannels, &vBananaChi2NdfLog[0]);
